    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Medical)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique can be performed even when it isn't your turn, though doing so will consume the swift action of your next turn, and must be used within 1<br><br>round of the target's death. You must maintain physical contact while maintaining this technique, and while doing so the target's body is held in perfect stasis, allowing it to remain useful for techniques or abilities that only work on (very) recently deceased bodies.<br><br>Each round you concentrate on this technique, you suffer 1 temporary Constitution damage, which can only be healed by resting. When the technique ends, you become exhausted until all the Constitution damage taken this way is healed.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
